Do you talk about the privacy of colleagues?
There are no good ways to stop gossip spreading.
Who did what, with whom?
Or and why?
Don’t tell everyone your information (assumptions) about your colleagues’ privacy!
If a colleague shares his intimate secrets with you, don’t abuse his trust!
Bury the shared information in yourself and don’t discuss it with your colleagues in his absence even if your colleagues are also aware of it.
You say you're sick for no good reason?
