Don’t put it on account of the possible chaos in the office or your noisy colleagues!
Recognize it if you made a mistake and if it presented inconvenience to others, fix the fault!
Ask how you could fix your fault, fix the negligence!
Do you feel at home in the office?
Putting on a jog and slippers is comfortable at home but they are not suitable for the office!
Do not wear comfortable jogging even if your function allows it!
Don’t be neglected, respect your colleagues and yourself by dressing properly, and if your function requires it by wearing beautiful and elegant clothes, to go to work!
